Title: Zero Curvature Formalism of the 4D Yang-Mills Theory in Superspace
Authors: L.C.Q.Vilar, C.A.G.Sasaki and S.P. Sorella
Comments: 31 pages, LateX2e, final version to appear in J. Math. Phys
Report-no: UERJ/DFT-03/98
Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 40 (1999) 2735-2756
\\
  The supersymmetric descent equations in superspace are discussed by means of
the introduction of two operators which allow to decompose the supersymmetric
covariant derivatives as BRS commutators.
